        xh:
            "I-STEADY RED DisC: iimoto kufuneka zime emva komgca kwaye zingahambi de kufike i-disc eluhlaza kwaye kukhuselekile ukuhamba. Ukuba akukho phawu lokuhamba kwabahambi ngeenyawo olunikezelweyo, abahambi ngeenyawo kufuneka bame. <br/> I-STEADY YELLOW DisC: iimoto kufuneka zime emva komgca wokumisa kwaye zingahambi de kufike i-disc eluhlaza kwaye kukhuselekile ukuhamba. Nangona kunjalo, ukuba kunokuba yingozi ukuba uyeke kuba ukufutshane kakhulu kumgca ungahamba. Ukuba akukho phawu lokuhamba kwabahambi ngeenyawo olunikezelweyo, abahambi ngeenyawo kufuneka bame. <br/> IDEE YENDLELA YOKUGQIBELA: Iimoto zinokuhamba, kodwa kufanele ukuba zibonakalise nakwezinye iimoto okanye abahambi ngeenyawo esele bephakathi kwendlela. Ukuba akukho phawu lokuhamba kwabahambi ngeenyawo lubonelelwe, abahambi ngeenyawo banokuhamba.",
