        zu:
            "Lesi sibonakaliso sikhonjiswa ngaphansi kophawu olulawulayo, ngokwesibonelo ukubekelwa indawo ngebhasi. Kubonisa ukuthi ukubhuka kusibonakaliso sokulawula kusebenza isikhathi esilinganiselwe, nokuthi kusebenza kuphela ngezikhathi nezikhathi ezithile zeviki. Ngezikhathi ezithile ngaphandle kwalabo abashiwo ukubhuka akusebenzi.",
