            "Lesi sibonakaliso sikhonjiswa ngaphansi kophawu lokulawula. Kubonisa ukuthi ukubhuka kusibonakaliso sokulawula kusebenza isikhathi esilinganiselwe, nokuthi kusebenza kuphela ngezikhathi ezithile zosuku. Ngezikhathi ezithile ngaphandle kwalabo abashiwo ukubhuka akusebenzi.",
