        af: "(1) Binne 1,5 m van 'n brandkraan.",
        zu: "(1) Ungakapheli u-1.5m wegesi eshisayo.",
        xh: "(1) Ngaphakathi kwesiqingatha se-1.5m yesicimi somlilo.",
