        zu:
            "Hlukanisa phakathi kwezingozi ezihambayo nezihamba phambili; gcina imoto yakho ilungele ukuba semgwaqweni; yiba nomphathi ngenkathi ushayela uma unelayisensi yomfundi kuphela.",
        xh:
            "Ukwahlula phakathi kweengozi zokuhamba kunye nezesitishi; gcina imoto yakho ihamba ngendlela; Yiba nesuphavayiza ngelixa uqhuba ukuba unelayisensi yomfundi kuphela.",
